  - htop


vim - Vi IMproved Text Editor

- a: insert
- escape: back to normal mode
- shift + colon --> "write"
- shift + color --> "q"

- y + p --> yank and paste (copy lines)
- w - go to start of next word
- e -
- b
- v
- y
- d
- p


git
  - version control (can have all the diff versions made new/old)
  - consensus
  - can be remote or local
  - can be centralized or distributed
  - merge conflicts
